Destroy specific resource command --------> terraform destroy -target resourcename.usergivenresourcename 

install provider plugin -------> terraform init

view the plan -------> terraform plan

create infra -----> terraform apply

comments part in terraform code ----> /*     comments go here */

to see state file and view -----> terraform show

use varibale explicit ------> terraform plan -var="instacetype=t2.micro"


